      "content": "it just feels like there's no way to actually step back. if i stop, i lose everything i've worked for, but if i keep going, i just feel like i'm breaking apart more every day. there's no middle ground. it's like i'm trapped in this loop of constant failure and it's just exhausting to even wake up in the morning. i feel like i've run out of options to fix this.",
